verbose_text: Noteworthily the factor age < = 65 years seems to be a less strong predictor for testing for HER2 expression in our actual cohort in 2012 and 2013 compared to 2010 and 2011 and the maximum of 96% of patients tested at the age of 67 years in 2012 and 2013 compared to 74% of patients at the age of 57 years in 2010 and 2011.
